data.description: Here's a cute and well cared for, little money maker. Lower unit is the larger 2 bdrm, 1 bath unit w/ access to basement, laundry, patio and garage. Upper unit is also a 2 bdrm, 1 bath unit. Both units are in really good shape and full of charm. Building has long term renters and zero vacancy. Lots of opportunities here. You could house hack by living in one of the units and make money; or you could rent out both units and make money. Either way, you are making $$$. Lets house hack!
